Blender export

1. Make sure that the armature moves with the mesh in Pose mode
2. Mesh - make sure "Apply Modifiers" is checked, you DO NOT need to apply modifiers in the Wrench (Modifiers) for the mesh
3. Vertex Colors - Materials export all vertex colors and active vertex color when no material
4. No Shape Keys
5. Armature - check use rest position, leave all other options Unchecked
6. Skinning - bone influences 4 leave "Include all bone influences" unchecked, if you check this one it will mess up the mesh entirely
7. Animation - Mode - NLA Tracks
8. Rest & Ranges - All options unchecked
9. Armature - both checked (export all armature actions and reset pose bones)
10. No Sampling Animations - you can sample though it will not mess it up
11. No Optimize Animations - you can optimize it will not mess it up
12. Make sure Rest post matches the bind pose
